SUMMARY:Women's Connection | Tuesday Mornings // Spring 2026
DESCRIPTION:PROVERBS 31 \nWhen you think of the “Proverbs 31 Woman\,” what comes to mind? Is she a relatable woman\, or just an unattainable ideal? This 12-week Bible study reveals that the key to a woman’s success is her focus on the Lord. It is so basic\, so fundamental\, and so overlooked. Radical God-centeredness will shape everything else in your life. \nJoin us for weekly sessions on Tuesday mornings from January 20 – April 28 \n9:45 – 11:30A | MP3 \nNursery is included in the price and provided for those bringing children under the age of 5. \nClick Here to Register Now
URL:https://ggwo.org/ggwo-event/womens-connection-tuesday-mornings-spring-2026/2026-01-20/
CATEGORIES:Women
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ggwo.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Connect-Pro-31-Poster-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
