SUMMARY:Redeem Life Recovery
DESCRIPTION:In our Redeem Life Recovery Ministry you can gain freedom from life’s struggles\, hurts\, hang ups\, stubborn habits\, and emotional distress. We encourage you to come and keep coming every week of biblical teachings\, learning Bible principles for your daily life\, practical advice to help you in your challenges\, individual counseling\, group counseling\, develop friendships\, and have an awesome fellowship in the body of Christ. \nRecovery Ministry
URL:https://ggwo.org/ggwo-event/redeem-life-recovery/2026-04-24/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ggwo.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RL-Slide.jpg
